data.description: New and improved fresh paint ready to move in Pool Property that can be your Dream Home, located on an oversized corner lot (8200 sqft lot) great neighborhood on a peaceful street, this home can be the oasis you have been looking for. Home comes complete with 4 spacious bedrooms and 2 full baths & a attached 3 car garage. The master suite is spacious with a walk-in closet that opens to the back yard with pool access. Pool is gated for safety for your family. The back yard is spacious to entertain your family and friends with plenty of side yard on both sides. Lots of potential!!
